            "content": "Nasenza casually throws a panga over her shoulder to rather accompany us a few kilometers to show us where the path is. Fred woos her with questions and he giggles frequently. Three men her age come walking past us and they have an exchange in Xhosa that I would have paid good money to understand - it was definitely about it. ",
            "link": null
          },
