    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We push on out of there for the last bit of distance for the day. The amber sun is setting and we’re descending on shark point. We make our way down to the beach but there is not level ground to free camp on. The owner of the kraal told us to check out the bungalows there - so I try open the sliding doors. And… success! Two are open. To make things more auspicious there is a smouldering piece of wood that Damo turns into a full on fire. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "We push on out of there for the last bit of distance for the day. The amber sun is setting and we’re descending on shark point. We make our way down to the beach but there is not level ground to free camp on. The owner of the kraal told us to check out the bungalows there - so I try open the sliding doors. And… success! Two are open. To make things more auspicious there is a smouldering piece of wood that Damo turns into a full on fire. ",
