          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Emerging from the sleeping bag wakes us up fully. It’s a bit of a mad dash shove everything into bag and get to shelter. Inside the bungalow there are simple mattresses and a warmth that is more than comforting. Damo and I smoke a joint while watching the stars and settle into a warm sleep.",
